    MaterialSideNavCard, MaterialSideNavDrawer, MaterialSideNavMini, MaterialSideNavPush

    public class MaterialSideNav
extends MaterialWidget
implements HasSelectables, HasInOutDurationTransition, HasSideNavHandlers
    SideNav is a material component that gives you a lists of menus and other navigation components.

    UiBinder Usage:

     
 <m:MaterialSideNav ui:field="sideNav" width="280" m:id="mysidebar"  closeOnClick="false">
     <m:MaterialLink href="#about" iconPosition="LEFT" iconType="OUTLINE" text="About" textColor="BLUE"  />
     <m:MaterialLink href="#gettingStarted" iconPosition="LEFT" iconType="DOWNLOAD" text="Getting Started" textColor="BLUE"  >
 </m:MaterialSideNav>
    Author:
    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol
    See Also:
    Material SideNav, Material Design Specification, Pattern
